  "description": "From the manufacturer Dog Activity Snack Toys and Strategy Games from TRIXIE offer new mental challenges for your dog. Inside the intelligence toys, the reward is waiting for your dog. The trick is to find the right technique to open each hiding place. The classic snack ball also comes in lots of exciting versions. With dumbbells, jumper or roll, dogs of all sizes and ages enjoy the fast game to get a delicious reward. TRIXIE Snack Spinner The TRIXIE Snack Rollist the perfect toy for dogs of all age. It can be fillew with small suitable treats. The difficuly of the snack spinner is entry-level, so also dogs who are not familiar with agaility toys can get a familiar with the idea of the game quickly. Plastic/TPR Stable plastic core with quiet-running rubber coating 3 removable rods to regulate the amount of treats released Screw-on lid, thus easy to fill and to clean Play and train at once The Snack Rollcan be used as a playing tool for dogs, as well as a training tool. Playing with this item raises the awareness and also requires focus and concentration. Successful achievments are rewarded without delay, as the snacks fall right out of the roll.",
